      &lt;img alt="The 8BitDo Ultimate Mobile Gaming Controller for Android with a smartphone attached and being played in two hands." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_Mnhd-CxU3Ie3ol9dxAqTfanGiI=/0x0:1332x888/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73677907/8bitdo_1.0.jpg" /&gt;
