      &lt;img alt="The special edition Leica M Edition 70 camera with a lens and strap attached. Sitting next to it is a metal 35mm film container." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JXW98gQ3uqkuQRXUbHIVlOC_e9I=/0x251:6008x4256/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73677640/10332_Leica_M_Edition_70_hero_HiRes.0.jpg" /&gt;
