      &lt;img alt="Photo of a hand holding iPhone with new Siri and ChatGPT." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1cvEfhZBdY5v0CvwAHVpyQ-cenE=/0x0:2000x1333/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73677630/DSC08567_processed_2.0.jpg" /&gt;
